CAD Hub

TheCADMan aims to be a comprehensive learning hub for Computational Aided Design, covering industrial design theory, manufacturing design process, and international standards such as DIN and ISO.

Lifelong Learning

Let's shift our focus on Lifelong learning. Make it easy via TheCADMan providing centralized platform for students, enthusiasts, and professionals to learn & share knowledge about CAD.
